reviewText: I couldn't watch this video - it kept pausing to buff; I waited for 10 min and gave up.
I really enjoyed watching this. This is one of our favorite shows. Love Connie, And Deacon. We can't wait for the new season to start. Love how Gunner and Scarlet can change their accents.
Love the show, love the cast and love the characters!

I have become a fan of the PALEYFEST panels.
But I was also a fan of the Dick Cavett show.
Love my new kindle! Video s are fast. The picture is clear and sharp. Also a large variety of videos to choose from.
This is a wonderfully talented cast!  And they genuinely seem to like and respect each other.  Thoroughly enjoyed watching this!

I love Nashville. The story line is great the music is wonderful. Each character is unique and I am so disappointed when the hour is up. It is refreshing and I can hardly wait from week to week. Thank you for something good to watch.

Love the show, cast and the characters they create. Some of the best writing, acting, filming and producing on TV right now. Not to mention the music/soundtrack...great performances and terrific songs. Nashville is a must-see even if one does not love country music.

Have you noticed how many times Deacon has said he is sorry?  When will he learn?  I do enjoy this show and I enjoy the music.  Watching episode after episode made me realize how Deacon is always apologizing.  lol
I am a huge fan of Connie! She is fantastic!
Very interesting on how the show came about and some insight on the real people who play the characters.
I found it highly informative but I am a big fan of the show. Give insite into how the cast came together. Will watch it again.
Love the cast
More effort should have been made to give the characters an equal chance to speak.  We hardly heard from Avery.  P.S.  I'm not his mother.
Great to listen to.  Commentator not the best.
Loved it!

It was very interesting to the cast stars and producers ect to talk about how the show comes together. It also surprised me to learn that 2 of them have accents from different countries that they don't display on the show. Great event to watch.
Fun to hear everyone speaking with their normal accents! Not a "southerner" in the lot!
excellent, no complaints
While it goes on forever when streaming, it's cool, clean, interesting and insightful.  I recommend it to families.
Great to see the cast outside of the show.
Great show.  Can't wait for season 5
Great cast.
Really good to see these people interact with each other when not acting.  Also it's nice to get to know a bit of their real personalities.
I love this show. I've watched it from the beginning.

Great show and wonderful cast!  It's my favorite and can't wait to see the next week. I was in Nashville in 2000 and visited at Christmas  so a lot of the places they talk about I have seen. .awesome! !!
Love this show and it's always fun to hear some behind the scenes information from the actors.  Enjoyed this program and recommend it to anyone who is enjoying this show.
Love this show and all the beautiful music!!
